{"tid":636640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公屋住一世] 天水圍公屋300呎20萬裝修3間房全部雙人床 預埋個仔娶老婆三代齊住","createTime":"2018-04-21T05:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T10:04:55.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"cc5c249e74ae1818cc41b15d6d94c224fe897d86","tid":636640,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"在這個樓市瘋癲的年代，能夠獲得一間公屋，已算十分幸運。一名離婚婦人，連同年老父母，和十多歲的兒子，早前獲分配天水圍一個三百餘呎的公屋單位。女戶主明白，將來兒子結婚，很大可能買不了樓。所以堅決豪花二十多萬，將這個細單位變成三間房。將來兒子找到另一半，也可搬進來一起住。<br />\n<br />\n「他們三代人，都有長遠的打算。因為現在物價指數高，買樓要很多錢。拿到這間公屋，一定會住十多二十年以上。除了將單位裝修成三間房之外，還要每間房都擺放四呎的床。」裝修師傅黃達明說。<br />\n<br />\n每間房都要雙人床，就算將來有成員結了婚，也可一起住，「因為四呎的床，長遠來說，雖然母子現在是單身，日後如果他們找到伴侶，每間房也要住兩個人。因為老人家的想法比較實際點，及長遠一點，他們寧願廳細一點，也為下一代著想，讓他們結婚後，也暫時有地方住。」<br />\n<br />\n這一代的香港人，要解決居住問題，確要花點心思。<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180420/large/1524205493_74a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180420%2Flarge%2F1524205493_74a2.jpg&h=b9253d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180420/large/1524205498_9697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180420%2Flarge%2F1524205498_9697.jpg&h=89059416&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff860d85bcd21f35382be2f01fe953449fc1c6a6","tid":636640,"uid":41508,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abee832a2027eadcb67eeb3b5a37c9202331526d","tid":636640,"uid":67500,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"港豬一生為屋而勞，邊有時間反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bea51a7da9386191a4b0c77ff7cbc46a64e19c0","tid":636640,"uid":31320,"like":52,"dislike":8,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"坦白講，裝修得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家下住四人，遲下 Max 住六人<br />\n點都好過五六千蚊個月出去租劏房<br />\n尼廿萬洗得值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d2ee593ee385984264dfc08ef64bf740aa6ffe","tid":636640,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"千零蚊租 抵到爛啦"},{"pid":"1b7ea0085dffe6baae0d0c91854ec085ae24f95d","tid":636640,"uid":31320,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c1d2ee593ee385984264dfc08ef64bf740aa6ffe","tid":636640,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"千零蚊租 抵到爛啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:28:54.000Z","msg":"當 $2000月租，住三十年唔駛 80萬<br />\n加埋裝修 20萬，都係 100萬<br />\n<br />\n首期都唔夠俾可以住六個人三十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a0ea5186f83d1d8d3325d52dc6897b077ccb5e","tid":636640,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"又係到影少少吹奏豪裝公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9915e44b3fbaf62d2b256337e63034525a531cfe","tid":636640,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"講真住公屋真係好過一般中產<br />\n<br />\n如果一個中產家庭到退休都只係得一間自住私樓都幾頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea13b5a3137892a7b5cbcf2f0a62f708f87c9a2","tid":636640,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"真係賤民思想<br />\n預左世世代代住公屋<br />\n哎吔富戶都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7aa70d19b5074836a0d4b363be0a2cb826aa503","tid":636640,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"知個仔